description: La Vie Est Belle eau de parfum for women, a French expression meaning 'life is beautiful,'—joyful f emininity and happiness.

name: Uomo Intense Eau de Parfum
description: Uomo intense is a sensual and captivating scent, with a charismatic aura that leaves intense memories.

name: Sì Passione Eau de Parfum
description: Sì Passione Intense is a fragrance that captures the vibe of passion.

name: Valentina Eau de Parfum
description: Valentina marks out a solar, unexpected trail, classic yet modern. With attitude, sophistication an d unexpected characteristics, the bouquet of Valentina blends an irreverent Italian floral oriental in which each facet reveals a paradox.

name: Valentino Voce Viva Eau de Parfum
description: An ode to Valentino's multifaceted femininity!With origin in Rome, following the contrasting trails of Valentino, inspires Voce viva eau de parfum!A parallelism between the sound of the voice and the aroma of our fragrance!

name: Miss Dior Eau de Parfum
description: Adorn yourself with amazing floral scents thanks to Miss Dior's new Eau de Parfum.

name: Good Girl Eau de Parfum
description: Good Girl Eau de Parfum

name: Good Girl Supreme Eau de Parfum
description: Intensely seductive, Good Girl Eau de Parfum Suprême reinvents the iconic Good Girl fragrance with a daring new formula. Redefining the emblematic contrast of lights and shadows, it encourages us to connect with our rebellious side, so that we can embrace all facets of our personality. In the words of Carolina A. Herrera, Creative Director of Beauty “It’s so good to be Bad!”.

name: Very Good Girl Eau de Parfum
description: Very Good Girl takes you on a surprising olfactive journey, starting with top notes of playfully mi schievous redcurrant and exotic lychee, leading to a seductive heart of rose. Vetiver and vanilla base notes provide a surprising and contemporary finish.

name: CH Women Eau De Toilette
description: CH Women Eau De Toilette

name: Roses Greedy Eau De Parfum
description: Mancera Roses Greedy is a versatile feminine perfume that wears well year-round and remains spirite d all day long.

name: Instant Crush Eau De Parfum
description: The irresistible trio - rose, jasmine, amber - strikes again, in a rich mix of sensuality and roman ce.

name: Le Parfum Eau De Toilette
description: Le Parfum Eau De Toilette

name: Eau Demoiselle Eau De Toilette
description: The delicate grace of a rebel rose is at the heart of Eau Demoiselle de Givenchy.

name: CHANCE EAU TENDRE
description: An even tenderer interpretation of CHANCE. A delicate presence, an intensely feminine and enveloping trail. A new chance for the taking.

name: COCO MADEMOISELLE
description: COCO MADEMOISELLE Eau de Parfum Intense. The essence of a free and captivating woman. A woody and ambery oriental fragrance with a full-bodied character: sensual, deep and addictive.

name: COCO NOIR
description: COCO NOIR is the embodiment of a black that reveals femininity. The contemporary expression of a magnetic sensuality told in a modern oriental fragrance with luminous notes. A radical creation.

name: ALLURE SENSUELLE
description: ALLURE SENSUELLE is another olfactory interpretation of the ALLURE fragrance. A voluptuous variation with an intriguing and magnetic sensuality. A floral-soft-oriental fragrance that is revealed in a unique way on each woman. Because every woman has her own special allure.

name: BLEU DE CHANEL
description: An ode to masculine freedom expressed in an aromatic-woody fragrance with a captivating trail. A ti meless scent housed in a bottle of deep and mysterious blue.

name: Sauvage Parfum
description: A fragrance with a trail of animal Sandalwood and smooth Tonka Bean illuminated by the freshness of spicy Mandarin.

name: Dior Homme Intense Eau de Parfum
description: The quintessence of prestige and sophistication in a generous and powerful Eau de Parfum. Intense Iris, enhanced by a sensual amber facet and precious wood base, exudes its powerful charm. A sensual interpretation with a fragrant trail that is an invitation.

name: Black Opium Eau de Parfum
description: A modern, young & vibrant interpretation of addiction. BLACK OPIUM, a fragrance like a shot of adre naline, the necessary energy for a life more & more intense.

name: Explorer Man Eau de Parfum
description: Mont Blanc: effortlessly masculine, a woody, leathery, aromatic fragrance, bold and adventurous encapturing top notes of fresh bergamot, pomarose® & sage on heart notes of vetiver, leather & sandalwood, and a base of patchouli, ambrofix & akigalawood®. For the true explorer

name: L'Homme L'Intense Eau de Parfum
description: The magnetic power of L'Homme, now made even more irresistible with a provocative blend of woody, aromatic notes wrapped in a sensual suede accord.

name: Insignia Men Limited Edition Eau De Parfum
description: A uniquely modern signature embracing the mystery of the Middle East, CH INSIGNIA MEN is a luxurious limited edition fragrance for the Carolina Herrera Man. ,,CH INSIGNIA MEN is an unabashed show of intent, with the dark leather flacon covered with a resplendent gold 'CH' clasp, making the bottle as distinctive as the scent housed within. The golden bottle cap is concentric, featuring the 'CH' INSIGNIA proudly etched on top, reflective of the statement fragrance it represents.,,A majestic duet paints the tapestry of this masculine signature, with the 'liquid gold' of Oud adding weight to the luxurious base, while Patchouli lends the scent a more earthy edge. A floral green middle of Rose & Violet are revealed following a spicy opening of Cinnamon and bittersweet Saffron. ,,TOP NOTES: Spicy Saffron & Cinnamon,MIDDLE NOTES: Rose & Violet,BOTTOM NOTES: Vibrant Woods, Patchouli, Ciste, Cashmeran & Oud

name: Gucci Guilty Oud Eau De Parfum
description: Inspired by a walk in a mysterious forest, the scent is conveyed in an enigmatic blend of dark Ambery notes, Leather and natural Oud. The fragrance experience is exotic, warm smoky, sensual and leathery.

name: The Only One Eau de Parfum Intense
description: The Only One Intense by Dolce Gabbana is alluringly feminine and irresistibly seductive. Its unique signature scent lies in the surprising combination of dazzling gold orange blossom contrasted with hypnotizing black vanilla to create an intense and solar sensuality.

name: My Burberry Black Eau de Parfum
description: My Burberry Black travels back to a London garden at dusk, heavy rain contrasting with the warm and captivating flora.A floral oriental interpretation of the iconic Eau de Parfum with a sensual touch.

name: Acqua Di Gio Absolu For Men Eau de Parfum
description: Giorgio Armani marries fresh aquatic notes with warm woods to create Acqua Di Gio Absolu - a powerful scent that celebrates the union between man and nature. Marine notes swirl with warm patchouli, labdanum and tonka beans for a sensual twist on masculinity. The amber-coloured liquid is housed in a clear glass, topped with a cap made from sustainably sourced ash wood that creates a nice contrast with the metallic collar of the bottle.

name: Black Orchid Eau de Parfum
description: Tom Ford Black Orchid, with its rich dark accords and alluring potion of black orchids and spice, is both modern and timeless.

name: Ambre Eccentrico Eau De Parfum
description: Ambre Eccentrico envelops straight into the depth of the heart notes- amber wrapped in smoky benzoi n, addictive vanilla and mysterious patchouli. With no top or middle notes, it is immediately charismatic.

name: Bleu Turquoise Eau de Parfum
description: Bleu Turquoise offers a journey through fragrance - crossing borders it infuses Italy, the heart of Giorgio Armani's creativity, with India's spirit. Infused with key notes drawn from the scent of incense and Indian spice markets, evocative of the country's fusion of the spiritual with every aspect of life.

name: Stronger with you Absolutely Eau De Parfum
description: Emporio Armani's Stronger With You Absolutely Parfum is inspired by the power of absolute love. A r efined masculine fragrance, boosted by an addictive new rum accord.

name: 212 VIP Men Black Eau de Parfum
description: The 212 VIP universe has expanded with a new launch of 212 VIP Black, a masculine fragrance full of sensuality that’s born from the revolutionary spirit of the House and is the life of the most exclusive party

name: ALLURE HOMME SPORT
description: Allure to the extreme. A powerful and dynamic composition. An aromatic-musky fragrance like a rush of adrenaline.

name: Black Incense Malaki Eau De Parfum
description: A sumptuous addition to the Malaki Collection, Black Incense Malaki is Chopard’s tribute to the millenary tradition of royal Frankincense. This rich and powerful incense elixir unfolds in luxurious layers of bright spices, smoky dark woods and intensely aromatic oils and gums. Its addictive trail, layered with oud and warm leather notes, evokes royal fragrant ceremonies and exhilarating swirls of burning resins. Echoing the Maison’s Luxury Naturals Perfumery philosophy, the most exquisite quality of pure frankincense from Somaliland stands out at the heart of the composition, blended with a superb array of sustainably sourced natural ingredients.

name: Gold Incense HERRERA CONFIDENTIAL Eau De
description: A SCENT OF MAGICAL OPULENCE: Powerful and elegant, Gold Incense evokes memories from another time and place with a modern olfactive structure bringing together the mystic scent of tapestries imbued with centuries of incense smoke and the modern luxury of the Middle East. MYSTERIOUS WARMTH OF EASTERN BEAUTY: A blend of matter and essence, Gold Incense’s formulation blends seven notes to give the combination character. A resounding opulence for a fragrance of refinement, based on a Boswellia Sacra Incense accord that merges with Atlas Cedarwood and Labdanum to create a warm, intense, and fascinating trail. Marigold gives a top opening and delivers singular vibrancy, whereas a subtle Vanilla Caviar from Madagascar underlines and impression of opulence.

name: Flora By Gucci Eau de Toilette
description: Experience this more concentrated and captivating formulation of Gucci Floraa subtle, sophisticated, floral fragrance inspired by princesses from the past, present, and future. The Flora Donna is a young, classic, and refined woman with the 'Gucci edge' of power and sensuality. She is elegant, natural, and spontaneous. The first Flora scarf was exclusively designed for Princess Grace of Monaco in 1966 and soon became one of the most popular Gucci icons. This scent is an expression of the Flora legacy. Its seductive layers mirror the playful details and bright colors that channel the heart of a fashion empire.

name: My Way Eau de Parfum
description: My Way Eau de Parfum

name: Acqua Di Gio Profumo Eau de Parfum
description: This Armani beauty Eau de Parfum for men pairs marine accords and fresh bergamot with patchouli and incense for a profoundly intense and aromatic men’s fragrance.

name: Nuit New Eau De Parfum
description: This new fragrance brings a darker, more sensual dimension to the magnetism of the iconic La Nuit de L'Homme Eau de Toilette. THE STORY Dark, resolutely mysterious and sulphurous, the La Nuit De L'Homme Eau de Parfum man uses his power of seduction through his natural and casual confidence up to dawn. Succumb to the call of a night of intense, burning and mysterious seduction with La Nuit De L'Homme Eau de Parfum. OLFACTION A masculine, addictive and intense interpretation of the iconic La Nuit de L'Homme Eau de Toilette. Burning sensuality is reinvented in a trail of Sandalwood and Patchouli Essence. Like a magnetic shiver, the essence of grapefruit reinforces the vibrant nature of the cardamom. Between the power of attraction and the game of seduction, let yourself succumb to the incandescence of La Nuit De L'Homme Eau de Parfum.
